column5: Change of plans kept us close to home but we did OK, Dad & Cousin Pete caught 3 Walleye, 2 Pike & a few Bass, I didn't get any pictures of their catch, nothing huge but respectable SBK
nice job.  Hard taking pics of self with fish isn't it.
Ya it's a pain in the butt, my partner back out at the last minute so I thought I'd try it SBK
